<div class="tool" data-tool="what-is-my-ip">
  <div class="pane-group">
    <div class="pane-toolbar">
      <span class="pane-label">Your public IPv4 address</span>
      <div class="pane-actions">
        <button id="ip-copy-v4" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" type="button" disabled aria-label="Copy IPv4 address">Copy</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="ip-v4" class="pane pane-mono" aria-live="polite">Detected automatically when this page loads (requires JavaScript)</div>
  </div>

  <div class="pane-group">
    <div class="pane-toolbar">
      <span class="pane-label">Your public IPv6 address</span>
      <div class="pane-actions">
        <button id="ip-copy-v6" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" type="button" disabled aria-label="Copy IPv6 address">Copy</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="ip-v6" class="pane pane-mono" aria-live="polite">Detected automatically when this page loads (requires JavaScript)</div>
  </div>

  <p id="ip-error" class="field-error" role="alert"></p>

  <div class="action-row">
    <button id="ip-refresh" class="btn btn-primary" type="button" disabled>Check again</button>
  </div>

  <div class="pane-group">
    <div class="pane-toolbar">
      <span class="pane-label">Connection details</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="result-list" aria-live="polite">
      <li>
        <span class="badge">TLS version</span>
        <code id="ip-tls" style="flex:1">–</code>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="badge">Cloudflare WARP</span>
        <code id="ip-warp" style="flex:1">–</code>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="badge">Answered by</span>
        <code id="ip-source" style="flex:1">–</code>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p class="field-hint">
    What this reveals: every site you visit sees this address, and can map it to
    your ISP and an approximate, city-level location — that mapping is what a
    VPN replaces with its own address. This page performs no location lookup:
    the only network request is the IP echo described in the privacy badge above.
  </p>
</div>

<script src="./client.ts"></script>
